{"tid":477893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過減肥熱包","createTime":"2017-11-23T12:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T00:00:25.000Z","uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c72230ba2b33440e82744aacceb467e436c9517c","tid":477893,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:59:52.000Z","msg":"老母有個朋友介紹佢用 減肥敷包貼肚用的<br />\nSend 曬圖出黎話好好多人瘦好多咁<br />\n見我肥所以迫我用埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOk 用唔係問題<br />\n但係佢規定1日最多只可坐800ml 水<br />\n渴撚到我仆街<br />\n痴撚線 講緊一日飲一支維他水咁多<br />\n有冇撚病呀？<br />\n<br />\n有冇功效？<br />\n我最近好急切要減肥做兄弟<br />\n一星期跑幾晚步實有瘦嫁<br />\n<br />\n而家係屋企老母見到我飲水 好似見我食煙咁<br />\n係咁叫我唔好飲咁多水<br />\n<br />\n請問各巴絲有冇用過？<br />\n係咪唔飲水用先有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/205948_0c4d44aae8e88a753d67e8547bc0cf44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F205948_0c4d44aae8e88a753d67e8547bc0cf44.jpg&h=432f2de5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"803044af761a9d7e5156d022dc64f141463826e2","tid":477893,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T13:14:01.000Z","msg":"其實係咪美圖秀秀都做到以下效果？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/211348_4070998f10ebde3dd3320e3e18daa583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F211348_4070998f10ebde3dd3320e3e18daa583.jpg&h=9c45a37a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/211353_cc3dc84a76e9d3537c95024e83f556f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F211353_cc3dc84a76e9d3537c95024e83f556f1.jpg&h=a8f19961&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53669bbc696108f127301dab9a838f935684eb3b","tid":477893,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ce0129bb63e4b957695ca9fa91cf01362661b6","tid":477893,"uid":72932,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係你就好肥好絕望 一係你就好蠢<br />\n點解會信支那效果圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求其用英文google下how to lose weight 都知道應該點做<br />\n點解你會覺得唔飲零卡路里嘅水 貼幾塊暖包就減到大肚腩"},{"pid":"14f497dd95f8bb3c5af14412a075a6db11d5a50e","tid":477893,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:53:42.000Z","msg":"On9 減唔到脂肪架 垃圾黎 人體飲唔夠水 對健康仲差"},{"pid":"eb77759e6c59b9acc03b697239383c849bee6a21","tid":477893,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T00:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係你就好肥好絕望 一係你就好蠢<br />\n點解會信支那效果圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求其用英文google下how to lose weight 都知道應該點做<br />\n點解你會覺得唔飲零卡路里嘅水 貼幾塊暖包就減到大肚腩</blockquote><br />\n可能我老母對我好絕望掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個人梗係唔撚信<br />\n都話被迫用"}]}